00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Welcome everyone to AI-Assisted Software Development with GitHub Copilot.

00:00:05.001 --> 00:00:12.000
Today we'll explore how AI can enhance your development workflow
and increase productivity.

00:00:12.001 --> 00:00:18.000
Let's start with the basics. GitHub Copilot is an AI pair programmer
that helps you write code faster.

00:00:18.001 --> 00:00:25.000
It's powered by OpenAI's Codex model and trained on billions of lines
of public code.

00:00:25.001 --> 00:00:32.000
The first topic we'll cover today is setting up your development environment
for AI-assisted coding.

00:00:32.001 --> 00:00:40.000
You'll need Visual Studio Code or a JetBrains IDE, and a GitHub Copilot
subscription.

00:00:40.001 --> 00:00:48.000
Let me show you how to install the Copilot extension and configure it
for optimal performance.

