00:04:10.001 --> 00:04:18.000
Notice how Copilot suggested both positive and negative test cases.

00:04:18.001 --> 00:04:26.000
This brings us to our final topic: security considerations when using
AI-assisted development.

00:04:26.001 --> 00:04:34.000
While Copilot is powerful, you should always review its suggestions
for security issues.

00:04:34.001 --> 00:04:42.000
Never blindly accept code that handles sensitive data like passwords
or authentication tokens.

00:04:42.001 --> 00:04:50.000
Always use established security libraries and patterns rather than
rolling your own.

